      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-white/80 mb-8">
        <span class="bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10">6+ Years Experience</span>
        <span class="bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10">Enterprise Solutions</span>
        <span class="bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10">Data & AI</span>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-6 mt-2 max-w-md">
         <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium tracking-wide">
          Also: Founder, prnvp&co <span class="text-gray-600">(Advisory Context)</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
